
1. implement inter thread communcation by creating banking 
   methods like deposit and withdraw.

2. create a java program to read n print the content to/from the file
   Note: display two options 1 for store data 2 for print data,
   if user press 1 then read the data from console and store it in file, 
   if user press 2 print the data from the file

3. Write a Java program to read contents from a file into byte array.

4. Write a Java program to store text file content 
   line by line into an array.

5. Write a Java program to read first 3 lines from a file.
